Description: Cypress Semiconductor introduces the SPARCore series of SPARC CPUs that provide one or two on-board processors and built-in single or multiprocessing functions. The CYM6001K, CYM6002K and CYM6003K make system upgrades as easy as changing daughterboards and loading a multiprocessing operating system. The CYM6001K has one SPARC CPU and works in single-processing environments, the CYM6002K has two on-board SPARC processors, and the CYM6003K has one SPARC processor but includes a multiprocessing cache-controller and memory-management unit for plugging multiple modules into a chassis.
